247
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:27,459
Usually, showing siya kung saan-saan.

248
00:14:27,460 --> 00:14:29,340
Ako ang pinakamalaking biktima.

249
00:14:31,380 --> 00:14:32,580
gutom ka ba?

250
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:34,700
Tara kain na tayo.

251
00:14:35,420 --> 00:14:36,340
Tara na.

252
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:38,700
Umupo sa upuan ng karangalan.

253
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:41,419
salamat po.

254
00:14:41,420 --> 00:14:42,540
Ito ay wala.

255
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:44,980
Heto, subukan mo muna ito.

256
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:47,540
Keso kalabasa.

257
00:14:57,540 --> 00:14:58,979
(Xu Wanxin)
(Paano mo masasabi)

258
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:01,500
(kung may nagkakagusto sayo?)

259
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:12,499
(Xi)
(Kapag lalaki at babae)

260
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:14,500
(simulan ang pagsubok sa isa't isa.)

261
00:15:14,780 --> 00:15:15,699
(Bakit?)

262
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:17,420
(Feeling a spark?)

263
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:19,699
(Hayaan mo akong hulaan.)

264
00:15:19,700 --> 00:15:21,419
(Ito ay isang taong malapit sa iyo.)

265
00:15:21,420 --> 00:15:23,860
(Ang kanyang pangalan ay Shen Gu.)

266
00:15:25,140 --> 00:15:26,900
(Xu Wanxin)
(Magandang hula.)

267
00:15:29,838 --> 00:15:35,038
(Xi: Hoy, Wanxin.
Nahuhulog ka ba kay Shen Gu?)

268
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:01,060
Hello?

269
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:02,460
Hello?

270
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:04,220
Nakabalik ka na?

271
00:16:04,900 --> 00:16:06,060
nasa baba na ako.

272
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:24,420
Gusto mo bang kumuha ng kagat sa gabi?

273
00:16:26,380 --> 00:16:27,500
Oo naman.

274
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:12,960
♪Ngayong gabi ay bumuhos ang ulan ng mahina at mabagal♪

275
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:20,040
♪Pagsasama sa mga titik na hindi pa nababasa
inaanod sa hangin♪

276
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:26,120
♪Tumalikod ka at tumingin sa akin♪

277
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:32,760
♪Sa parehong mga mata ay pamilyar na luha
tahimik na lumitaw♪

278
00:17:33,600 --> 00:17:39,240
♪Parang ang dami naming dinala♪

279
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:46,000
♪Napakaraming tanong ng oras mismo
hindi maipaliwanag♪

280
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:52,440
♪Sa sandaling pumasok ka sa buhay ko♪

281
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:59,400
♪Ang bawat panaginip ko ay naging isang bagay
Gusto kitang makasama♪

282
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:06,760
♪Ilang letra na ang naisulat ko
para lang sayo?♪

283
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:12,560
♪Kung naririnig mo lang talaga
ang gustong sabihin ng puso ko♪

284
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:19,599
♪Mula sa buhay na ito
walang distansya ang makapaghihiwalay sa atin♪

285
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:22,479
♪Ang pangakong binitawan natin♪

286
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:26,159
♪Hahanap ng paraan upang matupad
isang araw♪

287
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:32,759
♪Pero gusto ko pa
kaysa sa panandaliang titig na iyon♪

288
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:39,160
♪Hindi ko pa rin narinig ang sagot mo♪

289
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:45,879
♪Maari pa ba nating isulat muli ang wakas
magkaharap tayo?♪

290
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:51,000
♪Kapag nagsimulang lumingon sa iyo ang mga pagsisisi
maririnig ang lahat♪

291
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:54,480
♪Lahat ng naghahatid sa akin pabalik sa iyo♪

